Halcyon Investments, a New York riskarbitrage and securities dealing partnership, told theSecurities and Exchange Commission it has acquired 288,000shares of Cyclops Corp, or 7.1 pct of the total outstanding.    Halcyon said it bought the stake for 26.1 mln dlrs as partof its ordinary risk arbitrage and securities trading business.Other than that, the firm said there was no specific purpose inits purchases.    Halcyon said it might buy more stock or sell some or all ofits current stake. It said it bought the bulk of its stakebetween Feb 6 and March 13. Reuter&#3;